# Treat these as binary so Git never applies end-of-line conversion. Under
# core.autocrlf=true, Git would otherwise rewrite LF to CRLF inside these files
# on checkout and corrupt them (notably the committed demo inspection PDFs).
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.parquet binary
*.xlsx binary
